text: Clinuropsis is a genus of extinct sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks unassigned in the superfamily Conoidea.Bouchet, P. (2015). Clinuropsis Vincent, 1913 †. Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species at http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id;=432432 on 2015-02-22 ==Species== Species within the genus Clinuropsis include: * Clinuropsis dictyota (Sysoev, 1997): synonym of Lusitanops dictyota Sysoev, 1997 ==References== Category:Conoidea Category:Monotypic gastropod genera
